Zainab Damilola Alabi (ka amụrụ n' ụbọchị nke iri na isii n'ọnwa Ọktoba 2002) bụ onye egwuregwu badminton nke Naijiria. O sonyere na nnukwu ihe omume badminton na mpaghara na mba ụwa

Dị ka onye egwuregwu na-eto eto, o ritere ọla nchara atọ na 2018 African Youth Games nke emere na Algiers, Algeria. Alabi ritere ọla nchara nke ụmụ nwanyị na 2019 African Championship, yana ọla edo nke ndị otu na 2019 Rabat African Games.
